How to create a GUI Program

- Define a Container (like JFrame)
- Identify the components that will be needed for the UI (like JButton, JLabel, JTextField)
- Define the Layout through which you will add the components to the Container (like FlowLayout etc)
- Create the components
- Add the components to the container using .add method in Container
- Identify the actions you want to perform when components are interacted with (like button clicks, entering in text field etc)
- Create Listeners to perform actions when these components are clicked
